{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"25b343409f","title":"上海市委关于反右派斗争指示","origin":"上海市档案馆，B163-2-482，第13-18页。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"f9ac3258ac","index":0,"year":1957,"month":7,"day":27,"articleId":"25b343409f"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"994fc035d4","name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"7b63370e0d","type":"title","text":"上海市委关于反右派斗争指示","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25b343409f"},{"id":"feb2bda1c3","type":"subtitle","text":"[1957年7月27日各公司领导小组长会议刘局长传达市委关于反右派斗争指示]","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25b343409f"},{"id":"d7014f9ce5","type":"subtitle","text":"对工业部门的意见","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25b343409f"},{"id":"0042c46bd7","type":"paragraph","text":"1、工业部门的学习应以整风为主","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25b343409f"},{"id":"1e2429e5fb","type":"paragraph","text":"2、原来的部署是边学边“放”，“放”透了的单位是反右派，没有“放”透的就边学边“放”，未“放”的就“放”；以反右派为主来“放”的，这是我们对整风精神认识不足，因此应该以整风为主来“放”。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25b343409f"},{"id":"2584e0d133","type":"paragraph","text":"是否是反右派斗争停止了，半途而废了呢？不是，毛主席曾指示：(把党搞好(争取中间派搞臭右派","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25b343409f"},{"id":"f2a49a07a1","type":"subtitle","text":"当前的做法：","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25b343409f"},{"id":"01b41b277f","type":"paragraph","text":"1、先将反右的工作结束一下，作一小结","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25b343409f"},{"id":"56ca71803e","type":"paragraph","text":"2、继续“放”，但不要认为“放”是为了反右派，“放”的过程中有右派就反，没有就整风","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25b343409f"},{"id":"ebb47f81af","type":"paragraph","text":"3、不要怕乱，“放”得越充分越透越好，也不要怕起副作用，“放”出问题也没什么，将来可以“消毒”批判，因此要求党员副科长以上干部要硬着头皮听。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25b343409f"},{"id":"f6545a6c34","type":"paragraph","text":"4、做法：可以点先行，转的时候要将新提意见加以分析向群众作交代，对过去学习也应加以总结，错的意见也不一定介积，重点是使大家敢于进一步发表意见帮助党整风，中间分子的工作继续要争取，“放”的时候大体上三个星期即可","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25b343409f"},{"id":"44310acfe7","type":"paragraph","text":"整风与反右同时进行，过去以反右派为主，现在是整风为主，将来有右就反。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25b343409f"},{"id":"622fe0570f","type":"subtitle","text":"提意见规定：","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25b343409f"},{"id":"f81f787734","type":"paragraph","text":"1、工作整风两不误","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25b343409f"},{"id":"70d7800276","type":"paragraph","text":"2、除了规定整风的时间外，不得另占工作时间","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25b343409f"},{"id":"1499676a1f","type":"paragraph","text":"3、大字报只规定在本机关内贴，不得贴在机关外面","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25b343409f"},{"id":"65123445bd","type":"paragraph","text":"4、要求群众什么意见都可提，但要服从领导","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25b343409f"},{"id":"ac5024c0d7","type":"paragraph","text":"5、对干部要求什么意见都要听，但工作要负责","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25b343409f"},{"id":"d03ee1c66d","type":"paragraph","text":"6、工作还规定一条：只准动口不准动手","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25b343409f"},{"id":"c1aa8835e0","type":"paragraph","text":"提意见后进入第二阶段工作：开始明辨是非。对意见可分三类：（1）正确的（2）错误的（3）右派的","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25b343409f"},{"id":"14818835dc","type":"paragraph","text":"首先明辨领导的是非；其次进一步明辨群众中的是非，如极端民主，自由主义等。经过明辨是非，然后进一步开展反右派斗争。","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25b343409f"},{"id":"ea34e26668","type":"paragraph","text":"是非解决了就应该召开全体干部大会，总结这一阶段工作。","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25b343409f"},{"id":"9d5e04b74e","type":"paragraph","text":"这个工作结束后，党内整风就正式开始，在党内进一步明辨是非，采取和风细雨的方式。因此党内的问题不必过早下结论。","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25b343409f"},{"id":"06c37a06bd","type":"paragraph","text":"以上发扬民主到总结大体上一个半月左右。","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25b343409f"},{"id":"b79b60767a","type":"subtitle","text":"对公司的意见：","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25b343409f"},{"id":"16afe7ffc7","type":"paragraph","text":"1、不要乱斗","index":25,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25b343409f"},{"id":"76bf782e87","type":"paragraph","text":"2、局里应该帮助干部下楼，能解决的问题先解决","index":26,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25b343409f"},{"id":"7623a9042f","type":"paragraph","text":"3、应该抓紧工资改革，坛展节约，一边再搞学习。","index":27,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25b343409f"},{"id":"2b113bcffa","type":"subtitle","text":"马天水同志的几点意见：","index":28,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25b343409f"},{"id":"2c24c3e29d","type":"paragraph","text":"1、工厂要充分发动群众帮助党整风，这样可以暴露群众思想，并要充分发扬民主，这样的好处（1）时间可以缩短，但不能搞久（2）问题也可一针见血。","index":29,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25b343409f"},{"id":"167022a248","type":"paragraph","text":"2、要不要分批？从几方面看，不加强领导就“放”不开，因此必须分批，放了后如何半夜要事前也准备一切错误意见要澄清，澄清是非也必须要分批，加强领导。","index":30,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25b343409f"},{"id":"bf7ff81613","type":"subtitle","text":"3、做法：","index":31,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25b343409f"},{"id":"e65f7f5fd9","type":"paragraph","text":"（1）骨干要交代底（骨干指党员副科长以上干部）","index":32,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25b343409f"},{"id":"04f8809d06","type":"paragraph","text":"（2）有些似是而非的意见交群众讨论","index":33,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25b343409f"},{"id":"6b9266be7a","type":"paragraph","text":"（3）错误意见要批判","index":34,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25b343409f"},{"id":"5722a0cc71","type":"paragraph","text":"（4）有右就反","index":35,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25b343409f"},{"id":"bbb7a586e7","type":"paragraph","text":"（5）党群一起反","index":36,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25b343409f"},{"id":"f42162f647","type":"paragraph","text":"4、前一阶段因闹事不能充分发扬民主，现在闹事已基本停止，因此可以充分发扬民主。","index":37,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25b343409f"},{"id":"3ccb36fe83","type":"paragraph","text":"5、转的方法：有斗争对象的不要转，属一般的学习可以转，转的阶段时间一个礼拜左右。","index":38,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25b343409f"},{"id":"dc614a0dfe","type":"paragraph","text":"6、工厂规定的纪律：","index":39,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25b343409f"},{"id":"455e39e7eb","type":"paragraph","text":"（1）不能耽误生产","index":40,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25b343409f"},{"id":"886f0fd4e4","type":"paragraph","text":"（2）生产听指挥","index":41,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25b343409f"},{"id":"7a1e181dd6","type":"paragraph","text":"（3）不能搞到厂外出","index":42,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25b343409f"},{"id":"11adb707d7","type":"paragraph","text":"（4）只准动口不准动手","index":43,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25b343409f"},{"id":"ba9adb0d57","type":"subtitle","text":"石英局长指示：","index":44,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25b343409f"},{"id":"46a3004b4a","type":"paragraph","text":"1、现在的思想情况是两个“恨”，却不够。一恨右派不够， 二恨自己的缺点不够。实际上这两个问题是一个问题，是阶级斗争的问题。","index":45,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25b343409f"},{"id":"04ad0efe1e","type":"paragraph","text":"2、活动的目的性有三个：（1）把自己整好（2）打垮右派（3）团结好群众","index":46,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25b343409f"},{"id":"e65469b76f","type":"paragraph","text":"3、活动的特征：整风与反右是双生子，是一齐出笼的，整风是正产物，反右是副产物，如果离开整风搞右派，右派更出不来，不能以反右而“放”右，也不是为反右而整风，而是要为整风而整风。","index":47,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25b343409f"},{"id":"342e8cd006","type":"paragraph","text":"4、情况：（1）“放”了的单位，工作上的缺点及党的缺点都暴露得不够，右派分子也暴露得不够，时不深不（2）没有放的单位进入反右学习，是不得进，不得入","index":48,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25b343409f"},{"id":"051f7f00ba","type":"subtitle","text":"5、总步骤：","index":49,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25b343409f"},{"id":"e5b1aa8732","type":"paragraph","text":"（1）以下星期为界限作准备，再下一礼拜要变","index":50,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25b343409f"},{"id":"49d2773ae4","type":"paragraph","text":"（2）整风鸣放和公司工改交叉进行","index":51,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25b343409f"},{"id":"25063fe10b","type":"paragraph","text":"（3）现阶段反右派斗争如何解决，反右可放一下，文件不必继续学习，小组开展自我检查，互相批评，不是右派分子的不要翻历史，不要登黑板报，就可以结束了","index":52,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25b343409f"},{"id":"4604a71c6d","type":"paragraph","text":"（4）大步骤有三个：（1）整风鸣放（2）改进工作及反右斗争（3）个人整风","index":53,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25b343409f"},{"id":"304a2312be","type":"subtitle","text":"6、发动整风鸣放","index":54,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25b343409f"},{"id":"41e579156a","type":"paragraph","text":"（1）右派分子暴露不出来，仍要继续整风","index":55,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25b343409f"},{"id":"c3f4939626","type":"paragraph","text":"（2）方式不局限，大字报，黑板报都可，让群众自由发表意见","index":56,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25b343409f"},{"id":"a9ce265e28","type":"paragraph","text":"7、整风鸣放后下一步骤，可考虑三个问题：","index":57,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25b343409f"},{"id":"0eeddc32ea","type":"paragraph","text":"（1）如何改进工作向群众交代","index":58,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25b343409f"},{"id":"acdd623190","type":"paragraph","text":"（2）考虑反右派斗争，关键在于是否有具体对象，没有的就算了，一般思想在整风中解决","index":59,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25b343409f"},{"id":"b085a6c8f0","type":"paragraph","text":"（3）个人整风","index":60,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25b343409f"},{"id":"ceb9203a25","type":"subtitle","text":"基层整风：","index":61,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25b343409f"},{"id":"6eeefea573","type":"subtitle","text":"1、工厂现存在的问题：","index":62,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25b343409f"},{"id":"a99ecc043b","type":"paragraph","text":"（1）工人成分不纯","index":63,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25b343409f"},{"id":"2d4ee530f1","type":"paragraph","text":"（2）一部分工厂未经民改、肃反","index":64,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25b343409f"},{"id":"cd03c42298","type":"paragraph","text":"（3）干部还未很好下楼，已产生一些报复情绪","index":65,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25b343409f"},{"id":"524ff45de6","type":"paragraph","text":"（4）科室人员还为“放”，问题很多","index":66,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25b343409f"},{"id":"e0ef3853b2","type":"subtitle","text":"2、做法：","index":67,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25b343409f"},{"id":"a82265f830","type":"paragraph","text":"（1）工厂不是反右是整风","index":68,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25b343409f"},{"id":"49098ca562","type":"paragraph","text":"（2）可以搞大字报，适合暴露，充分发扬民主，大放大鸣，集中暴露党和工作缺点","index":69,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25b343409f"},{"id":"f86c0321dd","type":"paragraph","text":"（3）工资福利问题如解决不了的，采取向群众摊牌的方法","index":70,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25b343409f"},{"id":"666bc6c81e","type":"paragraph","text":"（4）阿飞流氓要采取公开批斗","index":71,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25b343409f"},{"id":"2b9cabadac","type":"subtitle","text":"3、通过整风反不反右派","index":72,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25b343409f"},{"id":"63956258b4","type":"paragraph","text":"（1）党内外一齐改","index":73,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25b343409f"},{"id":"b5ed5f0713","type":"paragraph","text":"（2）右派有则反，没有则不反","index":74,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25b343409f"},{"id":"75770676d5","type":"subtitle","text":"4、闹事厂怎么办？","index":75,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25b343409f"},{"id":"b71e433521","type":"paragraph","text":"（1）采取总结形式的办法","index":76,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25b343409f"},{"id":"15d5425244","type":"paragraph","text":"（2）首先肯定闹事是好事坏，应肯定有些闹事整是有理由的","index":77,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25b343409f"},{"id":"652111fc2d","type":"paragraph","text":"（3）首先分清领导上的是非，错的工作自我检查，然后分清群众是非","index":78,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25b343409f"},{"id":"4b22bd6785","type":"paragraph","text":"（4）闹事头子：一种是坏分子，一种思想落后，思想问题靠教育，属于坏分子看具体情况","index":79,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25b343409f"},{"id":"d6d3512a95","type":"subtitle","text":"5、中小厂整风如何搞？","index":80,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25b343409f"},{"id":"82a6981169","type":"paragraph","text":"试验后再说，可能采取工作队的形式","index":81,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25b343409f"},{"id":"2458286cef","type":"paragraph","text":" 1957年7月29日纪录整理","index":82,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25b343409f"}],"page":{"id":"dff33d8da2","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25b343409f","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}